Introduction

NANO is a South Korean singer, songwriter, and music producer. He was formerly a member of the boy group HISTORY. Following the group's disbandment in 2017, he adopted the stage name NANO and pursued a career as a singer-songwriter. Currently, he leads the producer team VENDORS, which he co-founded with fellow HISTORY member Jang Yi Jeong. In 2023, NANO established his own music production company, BILLION MUSIC.
